Detailed Description

cvmx_sso_pp::_grp_msk

CSR reserved addresses: (24): 0x5040..0x50f8 CSR align addresses: =========================================================================================================== SSO_PPX_GRP_MSK = SSO PP Group Mask Register (one bit per group per PP)

Selects which group(s) a PP belongs to. A '1' in any bit position sets the PP's membership in the corresponding group. A value of 0x0 will prevent the PP from receiving new work.

Note that these do not contain QOS level priorities for each PP. This is a change from previous POW designs.
